Package: hyperliquid
Title: API Wrapper to the Hyperliquid Exchange
Version: 0.0.1
URL: https://dereckscompany.github.io/hyperliquid,
    https://github.com/dereckscompany/hyperliquid
BugReports: https://github.com/dereckscompany/hyperliquid/issues
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Dereck",
           family = "Mezquita",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "dereck@mezquita.io",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9307-6762"))
Description: R API wrapper to the Hyperliquid decentralised exchange supporting
    both synchronous and asynchronous (promise based) operations. Provides R6
    classes for market data, perpetual and spot trading, account management,
    transfers, and staking, with Ethereum-style wallet signing for the exchange
    endpoint.
